name: Quantum Tunnel of Love
description:
Made for My First Game Jam Summer 2020 Controls
  • Pause - M
  • Choose Answer - Mouse or WASD/arrow keys + enter
Dates: The Final Frontier

Thanks to advanced, reality warping technology, mankind has made contact with alien species across the galaxy and beyond; they have now taken the next logical step: Intergalactic Speed Dating!

Go on dates with various alien species, learn their interests, and make first contact with their hearts in QUANTUM TUNNEL OF LOVE

Come on, it's not rocket science... it's quantum physics!

rated T for Teen
